225
00:16:42,705 --> 00:16:44,174
<font color=#FFFF00>A--aku ikut.</font>

226
00:16:44,444 --> 00:16:46,115
<font color=#FFFF00>Presdir harus tetap di sini.</font>

227
00:16:46,115 --> 00:16:48,115
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan meninggalkan ayahmu sendirian...</font>

228
00:16:48,715 --> 00:16:51,115
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan hubungi aku kalau terpikir akan seseorang.</font>

229
00:16:56,154 --> 00:17:00,054
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan terlalu khawatir.
Bajingan itu pasti akan tertangkap.</font>

230
00:17:01,194 --> 00:17:04,565
<font color=#FFFF00>- Terima kasih.
- Sedang apa kau? Aku sibuk!</font>

231
00:17:12,105 --> 00:17:13,105
<font color=#FFFF00>Permisi?</font>

232
