<font color=#FFFF00>Seung Chul Oppa.</font>

237
00:18:03,954 --> 00:18:05,795
<font color=#FFFF00>Joon membalas surat darimu?</font>

238
00:18:09,125 --> 00:18:11,595
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pasti sibuk mencoba beradaptasi di Seoul.</font>

239
00:18:12,795 --> 00:18:14,964
