247
00:18:46,365 --> 00:18:48,704
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan pergi. Jangan menonton film.</font>

248
00:18:48,704 --> 00:18:49,704
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

249
00:18:50,275 --> 00:18:53,704
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah maksudmu soal ke bioskop secara berkelompok besok?</font>

250
00:18:53,744 --> 00:18:55,674
<font color=#FFFF00>Besok? Apakah besok?</font>

251
00:18:55,704 --> 00:18:58,174
<font color=#FFFF00>Ja-jangan pergi. Jangan pergi.</font>

252
00:18:58,174 --> 00:19:00,515
<font color=#FFFF00>Eii, Seung Chul.</font>

253
00:19:00,545 --> 00:19:02,444
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Bel sekolah berbunyi...</i></font>

254
00:19:02,444 --> 00:19:04,615
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sekolah kita akan mulai...</i></font>

255
00:19:04,615 --> 00:19:07,454
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jika terlambat, kita dapat masalah...</i></font>

256
00:19:08,625 --> 00:19:10,555
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Hyun Soo. Ayo kita pergi bersama.</font>

257
00:19:11,394 --> 00:19:14,224
<font color=#FFFF00>Ja--jangan. Jangan ke sana.</font>

258
00:19:14,224 --> 00:19:16,194
