<font color=#FFFF00>Oppa!</font>

261
00:19:20,504 --> 00:19:21,805
<font color=#FFFF00>Anak itu kenapa?</font>

262
00:19:22,605 --> 00:19:23,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan apa-apa.</font>

263
00:19:27,045 --> 00:19:28,244
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat itu,</font>

264
