267
00:19:40,154 --> 00:19:41,285
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mengenalnya?</font>

268
00:19:50,765 --> 00:19:52,194
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat SMP dulu,</font>

269
00:19:53,605 --> 00:19:55,934
<font color=#FFFF00>dia adalah teman dekat Oppa.</font>

270
00:19:57,105 --> 00:19:58,105
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku?</font>

271
00:20:00,944 --> 00:20:02,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia temanku?</font>

272
00:20:03,204 --> 00:20:05,615
<font color=#FFFF00>- Di mana dia sekarang?
- Bencana Time Mart...</font>

273
00:20:07,845 --> 00:20:08,984
<font color=#FFFF00>...menewaskannya.</font>

274
00:20:12,615 --> 00:20:13,625
<font color=#FFFF00>("Keluarga Korban Menuntut Kebenaran")</font>

275
00:20:13,625 --> 00:20:15,085
<font color=#FFFF00>20 tahun lalu,</font>

276
00:20:15,325 --> 00:20:18,325
<font color=#FFFF00>sebuah gedung perbelanjaan baru di Moojin runtuh.</font>

277
00:20:19,025 --> 00:20:20,694
<font color=#FFFF00>Di bioskop lantai lima gedung tersebut,</font>

278
00:20:21,765 --> 00:20:23,795
<font color=#FFFF00>para murid kelas tujuh dari SMP Moojin...</font>

279
00:20:23,865 --> 00:20:25,934
<font color=#FFFF00>...sedang menonton film bersama hari itu.</font>

280
00:20:26,065 --> 00:20:27,265
<font color=#FFFF00>Bencana itu...</font>

281
00:20:28,535 --> 00:20:31,704
<font color=#FFFF00>...menewaskan hampir 300 orang.</font>

282
00:20:37,815 --> 00:20:40,015
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun, meski jumlah korban jiwanya sebanyak itu,</font>

283
