322
00:22:46,904 --> 00:22:50,845
<font color=#FFFF00>Aigoo. Seandainya saja mereka mendengarkan cenayang cilik itu...</font>

323
00:22:53,214 --> 00:22:55,914
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa, kakakku menganggap Seung Chul...</font>

324
